These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, techno, disco
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | disco | pop | techno |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, epic, spy
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person watching epic movies is the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | epic     | scientific        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, water-polo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Sport         | water-polo     | cricket | snowboarding |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
House: tower, palace, victorian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the palace house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the tower house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the palace house is in an even position##4
4. the palace house is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| House   | victorian | palace  | tower  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
City: berlin, nizza, colone
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person traveling to berlin##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| City   | nizza | colone     | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, january, september
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday   | january | september | july   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, balloon-flower
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Flower           | marigold         | zinnia         | balloon-flower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, december, february
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Birthday   | december | february | october |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, funk
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep  | ambient  |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | water | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, parkour, sailing
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Sport       | parkour | sailing | handball   |

