.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, lavender, black
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes blue##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes black is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Color         | lavender | black | blue |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, mauve, red
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the australian is the person who likes red##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| Color     | mauve     | blue   | red        |

