.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, freelancer
1. the freelancer is on the right of the french##1
2. the fisherman is the dutch##1
3. the french is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | french  | canadian | dutch   |
| Job         | librarian | freelancer   | fisherman |

