.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, handball
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | handball | skateboarding |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

