.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, blue, turquise
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
4. the person who likes turquise is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Color   | azure  | turquise     | blue |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

