.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, kale, watermelon
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Food          | watermelon | cucumber | kale  |
| Hobby   | video-games      | magic-tricks  | puzzles |

