.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, pop, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre     | pop  | salsa   | techno |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 